Definition: any of various water-soluble compounds having a sour taste and capable of turning litmus red and reacting with a base to form a salt
Synonyms: adj, all, acidic, verb, perception, acidulate, acidify, change, compound, any, of, various, water-soluble, compounds, having, a, sour, taste, and, capable, turning, litmus, red, reacting, with, base, to, form, salt
Category: noun.substance
